*"Devojke su radovale kada su čule da će biti izlet." (The girls were delighted when they heard there would be a trip.)

*"Devojke su se uželele svojih porodica." (The girls missed their families.)

*"U parku su se igrala tri devojke." (Three girls were playing in the park.)

*"Devojke koje smo sreli bile su veoma ljubazne." (The girls we met were very kind.)

*"Devojke su nosile lepe haljine za večeru." (The girls were wearing beautiful dresses for dinner.)